author: Kam Dhillon
title: Here’s What Parisian Streetwear Heads Have to Say About Supreme x Lacoste
text:
Visit the original post to see all 12 images from this gallery. 
Location: Paris, France
Season: SS17
Key Looks: The BAPE x PUMA camo jacket is a trend-led look for spring (slide 7), the Supreme x UNDERCOVER coach jacket with some bleak renaissance visuals (slide 5), and that effective lesson in color-coordinating mustard (slide 6).
Editor’s Notes: Paris’ finest stepped out in a slew of Supreme’s greatest hits to join the snaking line on Rue Barbette for a chance to cop a piece from the brand’s latest collaboration with Lacoste. See below for a video documenting the day’s goings-on.

You’ve seen what looks Paris wore, now check out what New Yorkers wore to Supreme’s Lacoste drop .
